    <item>
      <title>Gym &amp; Food</title>
      <link>https://mezpahlan.github.io/blog/2012/10/07/gym/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 07 Oct 2012 11:31:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://mezpahlan.github.io/blog/2012/10/07/gym/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This past month I&amp;rsquo;ve been trying out a new exercise routine. It involves high intensity interval training and more
weights than I would normally do. The idea is to stimulate my body to have a higher proportion of lean muscle than fat.
So far it has worked well! Muscle seems to burn off a lot more excess weight whilst I&amp;rsquo;m not at the gym than long
distance running that I used to do.&lt;/p&gt;
