      <description>&lt;p&gt;Ingredients:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Smoked Salmon&lt;br&gt;
Fresh tagliatelle&lt;br&gt;
Single cream&lt;br&gt;
Yummy cheese&lt;br&gt;
Salt&lt;br&gt;
Pepper&lt;br&gt;
Herby stuff (dill, etc)&lt;br&gt;
Egg&lt;br&gt;
Paprika (optional)&lt;br&gt;
Olive oil&lt;br&gt;
Butter&lt;br&gt;
White wine (optional)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Instructions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Crack egg into bowl and whisk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Put tagliatelle into pot and simmer with hot water with olive oil&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add cream to egg whisk and whisk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add the herby stuff to the egg and cream whisk and whisk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Add salt and pepper to the egg, cream and herby whisk and whisk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Grate cheese into the egg, cream, herby stuff, salt and pepper whisk and whisk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flake salmon into the egg, cream, herby stuff, salt, pepper and cheese whisk and whisk&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Drain tagliatelle and mix with the bowl of whisk with butter and a glass of white wine.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enjoy!&lt;/p&gt;
